@startuml
title AI Intelligence Layer - OpenAI Integration

participant "AI Processor" as AI
participant "OpenAI Client" as Client
participant "OpenAI API" as OpenAI
participant "Score Calculator" as Score
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

AI -> AI: 1. Receive aggregated scan JSON

AI -> AI: 2. Build constrained system prompt
note right
  "Return ONLY JSON with:
   - security_score (0-100)
   - findings array
   Each finding: severity, title,
   plain_english_explanation,
   remediation_steps"
end note

AI -> Client: 3. createRequest()
Client -> OpenAI: 4. POST /v1/chat/completions
OpenAI -> OpenAI: 5. Process (2-5 sec)
OpenAI --> Client: 6. Return JSON
Client --> AI: 7. Response body

AI -> AI: 8. Parse & validate JSON
AI -> AI: 9. Extract findings

AI -> Score: 10. calculateWeightedScore
Score -> Score: 11. e.g 100 - penalties
Score --> AI: 12. Return final_score

AI -> DB: 13. BEGIN TRANSACTION
AI -> DB: 14. INSERT findings (batch)
AI -> DB: 15. UPDATE scans SET status='completed', score
AI -> DB: 16. COMMIT

@enduml